---
title: Roast Chicken and Creamy Pesto Sauce with kale and buttery potatoes
description: Succulent roast chicken breast is smothered in creamy pesto sauce, served alongside buttery potatoes and vitamin-rich kale in this nutritious recipe that's filled with flavour.
